    <briefdescription>
<para>A single step executed by the rendering pipeline. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A <ref refid="classLotus_1_1Renderer_1_1RenderPass" kindref="compound">RenderPass</ref> is a way to organize tasks in the render pipeline. This provides a base class that implementations will derive from to define rendering tasks. The rendering pipeline simply executes these passes in the order that they are registered. </para>
